headline: FS KKR Capital: Is The 12% Dividend Yield Sustainable?
summary: FSK offers an eye-catching 12.85% dividend yield and trades at a 7% discount to NAV. However, the dividend payout is looking increasingly at-risk. Read the full analysis on this BDC here.

headline: Global Atlantic Featured in Barron’s 100 Best Annuities Guide
summary: NEW YORK, July 28, 2025--Global Atlantic, a leading provider of retirement security and investment solutions and a wholly-owned subsidiary of KKR, announced its inclusion in Barron’s annual guide to the 100 Best Annuities, marking the firm’s fourth consecutive appearance in the article. The featured annuities include Fixed Index Annuity Income 150+ SE and ForeStructured Growth II Advisory, a registered index-linked annuity.
